  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Week 2 of "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "Summer into AI 2026"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " hosted by "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "@advisoryhour"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " — theme: Red, White & Boom."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "New York City, 1778. You are Agent 355 — handler for America's most successful spy ring. Each round, a cipher dispatch arrives from the field: Abraham Woodhull (C——r) in Setauket, Robert Townsend (C——r Jr.) in Manhattan, Austin Roe on horseback between them. Claude generates the dispatch in authentic Culper tradecraft: numbered locations, coded names, invisible-ink shorthand. You must read the cipher, choose your response from three options, and relay the intelligence to General Washington (Agent 711) before it goes stale."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Worth noting alongside this: "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "The Patriot Gazette by another Week 2 entrant"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " where that demo generates propaganda you read, this one generates intelligence you must decode and act on — the AI is the enemy as much as the tool"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How the AI works"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Two Claude endpoints drive the loop. The "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "dispatch endpoint"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " generates each cipher message using the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "generate_dispatch tool"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Claude produces a dispatch in period Culper tradecraft, its plain-English translation (shown only after you decide), three plausible response options, the correct option ID, and a historical context note."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "evaluate endpoint"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " assesses your decision using the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "evaluate_decision tool"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": it returns success/failure, an outcome narrative, intelligence gained for Washington's campaign, whether your spy's cover status is still "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "active"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", compromised, or captured, and a historical debrief on what the coded phrases actually meant."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The codebook is always visible as you play: 711=Washington, C——r=Woodhull, C——r Jr.=Townsend, John Bolton=Tallmadge, 10=NYC, 20=Setauket, 30=Oyster Bay. Reading the cipher correctly — not just picking randomly — is what wins."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How to play"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Read each cipher dispatch using the permanent codebook sidebar — the correct answer is in the text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Choose from three response options: relay, wait, or act on the intelligence"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "See the plain-English translation revealed after your decision"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Win 3 of 4 dispatches while keeping the network active to complete your mission"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
